Wheeljack::

Jackie's powerful sound filters let him hear things that most people 
can't, and he tracks down the infant's cries.  Not knowing much about 
child care, he improvises.  The Autobot cradles the baby gently in 
his arms, playing an Earth lullaby on his built-in sound system.
